pullRequest.body:
This PR is a part of our porting work of the dimension theory part of @erdOne 's lean3 repository [here](https://github.com/erdOne/lean-AG-morphisms). In this PR, we ported some more lemmas relating to Artinian properties, establishing some connections between Artinian properties and Noetherian properties.

Co-authored-by:  
Andrew Yang @erdOne 
Wanyi He @Blackfeather007 <2100017455@stu.pku.edu.cn>
Shouxin Zhang @ShouxinZhang <202013140018@nuist.edu.cn>

- [ ] depends on: #22356

---
